properties.name: spring.ai.model.chat
properties.description: The primary ChatModel to autoconfigure. If not set, each ChatModel auto-configuration is enabled by default.

properties.name: spring.ai.model.embedding
properties.description: The primary EmbeddingModel to autoconfigure. If not set, each EmbeddingModel auto-configuration is enabled by default.

properties.name: spring.ai.model.embedding.text
properties.description: The primary EmbeddingModel for text embeddings to autoconfigure. If not set, each text EmbeddingModel auto-configuration is enabled by default.

properties.name: spring.ai.model.embedding.multimodal
properties.description: The primary EmbeddingModel for multimodal embeddings to autoconfigure. If not set, each multimodal EmbeddingModel auto-configuration is enabled by default.

properties.name: spring.ai.model.image
properties.description: The primary ImageModel to autoconfigure. If not set, each ImageModel auto-configuration is enabled by default.

properties.name: spring.ai.model.audio.transcription
properties.description: The primary TranscriptionModel to autoconfigure. If not set, each TranscriptionModel auto-configuration is enabled by default.

properties.name: spring.ai.model.audio.speech
properties.description: The primary SpeechModel to autoconfigure. If not set, each SpeechModel auto-configuration is enabled by default.

properties.name: spring.ai.model.moderation
properties.description: The primary ModerationModel to autoconfigure. If not set, each ModerationModel auto-configuration is enabled by default.
